# Project Learnings

Before making changes to these files, read the relevant learnings:

- **`.learnings/architecture.md`** -- Production topology, server bundle pipeline, data persistence, WebSocket architecture, macOS constraints
- **`.learnings/gotchas.md`** -- Non-obvious pitfalls with Svelte 5 reactivity, Vite SSR externals, secure context APIs, ephemeral app bundles, and more

Read both files when working on build/deployment. Read `gotchas.md` when debugging unexpected behavior.
